document_title: Acyanotic congenital heart disease: Causes, symptoms, treatment
subsection_name: benh-tim-bam-sinh-khong-tim.json_0_What is acyanotic congenital heart disease?
subsection_content: Acyanotic congenital heart disease is a condition that involves abnormalities in blood flow. In this heart defect, blood contains enough oxygen but is not pumped throughout the body normally.
